==========================MODEL EXPLAINATION==========================

The User will Select 

(1) The Course, 
then the Departments will be sorted on the basis of the CourseID.

(2) The Department,
then the Semesters will be sorted on the basis of the CourseID & DepartmentID.

(3) The Semesters,
then the Subjects will be sorted on the basis of the CourseID, DepartmentID and Semester No.

(4) The Subjects,
then the books will be sorted on the basis of the CourseID, DepartmentID, Semester No., and SubjectID.